description:
WAGmob.com brings you on-the-go learning and reference for Physics.

App offers quizzes and tutorials to help you learn about Physics.

App is continuously updated based on your feedback. Your 100% satisfaction is guaranteed.

App tools include search feature.



Includes following tutorials:

Introduction to Physics,
Matter,
Motion,
Force,
Dynamics,
Gravitation,
Relativity,
Wave and Light,
Heat and Temperature,
Basics of Quantum Mechanics,
Chemical Kinetics,
Solutions,
Osmosis,
Electricity and Magnetism,
Radioactivity,
Thermodynamics,
Few Basic Laws,
Static and Current Electricity,
Introduction to Electronics,
Sound,
Properties of Sound Wave,
Doppler Effect,
Shock Waves and Sonic Boom,
Physical Constants,
Units,
Dimensional Analysis,
Formula Pack 1,
Formula Pack 2,
Formula Pack 3,
Formula Pack 4.


Includes following quizzes:

Quiz on Matter, Motion, and Force,
Quiz on Dynamics, Gravitation, Relativity, and Light,
Quiz on Heat, Quantum Mechanics, and Chemical Kinetics,
Quiz on Magnetism and Radioactivity,
Quiz on Thermodynamics and Electricity,
Quiz on Sound and its Properties,
Quiz on Physical Constants, Units, and Dimensions.



What is unique about WAGmob apps? 

1) A touch friendly, quick reference app, which is always in your pocket and always works (no data connection required)

2) A companion app for on-the-go, bite-sized learning

3) Offers value for money (A lifetime of free updates)

4) 300,000 paying customers from 175  Countries.



Our Vision: Provide on-the-go references that enable our customers to refer, learn and remember; easy to learn, more engaging and truly complete.

Our Mission: A WAGmob app in every pocket.

Please write to us. We would love to improve this app.
